Servers 

We offer a wide range of server products using our SPARC microprocessor, which are designed to be differentiated by their reliability, security and scalability. We also offer servers using microprocessors from Intel Corporation (Intel). By offering customers a range of microprocessors, we offer flexibility for customers to choose the types of hardware products that they believe will be most appropriate and valuable for their particular IT environments. 

